import React from 'react'; function Dashboard({ dailyData, expenses, activities }) { // Calculate total expenses const totalExpenses = expenses.reduce((total, exp) => total + parseFloat(exp.amount || 0), 0); // Calculate average mood if we have mood data const moods = dailyData.filter(item => item.mood).map(item => parseInt(item.mood)); const avgMood = moods.length ? (moods.reduce((sum, mood) => sum + mood, 0) / moods.length).toFixed(1) : 'N/A'; // Calculate total exercise time const totalExercise = dailyData.reduce((total, entry) => total + parseInt(entry.exercise || 0), 0); // Find most recent entries const latestDailyEntry = dailyData.length ? dailyData[dailyData.length - 1] : null; const latestExpense = expenses.length ? expenses[expenses.length - 1] : null; const latestActivity = activities.length ? activities[activities.length - 1] : null; // Format date for welcome message const today = new Date(); const options = { weekday: 'long', year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }; const formattedDate = today.toLocaleDateString(undefined, options); return (

Welcome to Your Personal Tracker!

Today is {formattedDate}. Track your daily activities, expenses, and well-being all in one place.

{dailyData.length}

Daily Entries

${totalExpenses.toFixed(2)}

Total Expenses

{avgMood}

Average Mood (1-10)

{totalExercise} min

Total Exercise Time

Recent Activity

Latest Daily Entry
{latestDailyEntry ? ( <>

Date: {new Date(latestDailyEntry.date).toLocaleDateString()}

Mood: {latestDailyEntry.mood}/10

Sleep: {latestDailyEntry.sleep} hours

Water: {latestDailyEntry.waterIntake} glasses

Exercise: {latestDailyEntry.exercise} minutes

Notes: {latestDailyEntry.notes}

) : (

No entries yet. Start tracking your daily stats!

)}
Latest Expense
{latestExpense ? ( <>

Date: {new Date(latestExpense.date).toLocaleDateString()}

Category: {latestExpense.category}

Amount: ${parseFloat(latestExpense.amount || 0).toFixed(2)}

Description: {latestExpense.description}

) : (

No expenses recorded yet. Start tracking your spending!

)}
Latest Activity
{latestActivity ? ( <>

Date: {new Date(latestActivity.date).toLocaleDateString()}

Activity: {latestActivity.name}

Category: {latestActivity.category}

Duration: {latestActivity.duration} minutes

Notes: {latestActivity.notes}

) : (

No activities recorded yet. Start tracking your activities!

)}
Quick Tips
  • Use the Daily Data tab to track your health and wellness metrics
  • The Money Tracker helps you categorize and monitor your expenses
  • Track how you spend your time with the Activities tracker
  • All data is stored locally in your browser and is not sent to any server
); } export default Dashboard;
